She leads the telecommunications growth topic worldwide. In 2015 Rocío was named one of 25 female business leaders by Handelsblatt, HuffPost and Edition F. author: Rocío_Lorenzo;
title: How diversity makes teams more innovative

aws-transcripts.transcript: 15 years ago, I thought that the diversity stuff was not something I had to worry about. It was something on older generation had to fight for. In my university, we're we're 50 50 male, female, and we women had often better greats. So well, not everything was perfect. Diversity in leadership positions. What Something that would happen naturally over time, right? Well, not quite well, moving up the ladder, working as a management consultant across Europe and the US, I started to realize how often I was the only woman in the room. And how are my genius? Leadership is still is many leaders I met so diversity as something to comply without off political correctness or miss case the right thing to do. But not that's a business priority. They just didn't have a reason to believe that diversity would help them achieve their most immediate pressing goals hit in the numbers, delivering the new product, the rial goals. They are measured by my personal experience. Working with diverse teams had been that while they require a little bit more effort at the beginning, they did bring fresher, more great if ideas.
